title: Large Bank Consumer Credit Card Originations: Original Credit Limit: 75th Percentile
notes: The 75th percentile credit limit among credit cards originated in the observed quarter. The original credit limit is the available credit limit at the time of origination. For more detail see: methodology (https://www.philadelphiafed.org/-/media/frbp/assets/surveys-and-data/y14/y-14-data-methodology)
